        <source>Score = PCAF Status (20% if signatory, 10% if mentioned) + Part A (40% if reported, 20% if partial) + Part B/C (15% if reported, 7.5% if partial) + Asset Classes (2.5% per class reported, 1.25% if partial).</source>
